  "prompt": "Will Pok\u00e9mon Sun and Moon only work with the New 3DS console?",
  "response": "No, **Pok\u00e9mon Sun and Moon** are not limited to the New 3DS consoles. They are compatible with all models in the Nintendo 3DS family, including:\n\n- **Original 3DS**\n- **3DS XL**\n- **New 3DS**\n- **New 3DS XL**\n\nWhile the New 3DS models offer enhanced performance and additional features (like extra control buttons and improved 3D capabilities), **Pok\u00e9mon Sun and Moon** will run on any of the above 3DS systems. You can enjoy the game regardless of whether you have the original 3DS or one of the newer variants.\n\n**Key Points:**\n- **Compatibility:** All Nintendo 3DS models can run Pok\u00e9mon Sun and Moon.\n- **Features:** New 3DS models might provide a slightly better experience due to enhanced hardware, but it's not a requirement.\n- **Purchasing Advice:** If you're considering buying the game and already have a 3DS system, you should be able to play it without needing to upgrade your console.\n\nFeel free to dive into the Alola region and enjoy your Pok\u00e9mon adventure on your preferred 3DS model!",
